---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/layout/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import BreadcrumbSchema from '../components/seo/BreadcrumbSchema.astro';
import { getSiteConfig } from '../config/getSiteConfig';

const siteConfig = getSiteConfig(Astro.locals.siteVariant);
const c = siteConfig;
const siteHost = new URL(c.url).hostname;
const addr = c.contact.address;
const addressLine = `${addr.street}, ${addr.city}, ${addr.state} ${addr.zip}`;

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { name: 'Terms of Service', href: '/terms/' },
];

const lastUpdated = 'May 5, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description={`Terms governing use of ${siteHost} and services provided by ${c.business.legalName}.`}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <BreadcrumbSchema items={breadcrumbs} />
  </Fragment>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />
  <section class="section legal-doc">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <header class="legal-doc__header">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="legal-doc__meta">
          {c.business.legalName} · {siteHost}
        </p>
        <p class="text-subtle">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </header>

      <p>
        These Terms of Service (&quot;Terms&quot;) govern your use of the website located at {siteHost}{' '}
        and any services provided by {c.business.legalName} (&quot;we,&quot; &quot;us,&quot; or
        &quot;our&quot;). By accessing our website or booking services with us, you agree to be bound by
        these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our website or services.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Services offered</h2>
      <p>{c.business.name} provides hair salon and beauty services including but not limited to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Precision haircuts</li>
        <li>Dimensional hair color</li>
        <li>Blonding and highlights</li>
        <li>Styling guidance and product recommendations</li>
        <li>Hair consultations by appointment</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Services are provided by appointment only.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Medical disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="legal-doc__important">
        <strong>IMPORTANT — PLEASE READ CAREFULLY.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        The content on our website is provided for informational purposes only and does not constitute
        medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Results shown in before and after photos, testimonials,
        or descriptions are individual and are not guaranteed. Your results will vary based on your hair
        history, current condition, home care, lifestyle, and other factors outside our control.
      </p>
      <p>
        Hair services carry inherent risks. A consultation may be conducted before color, blonding, or
        major style changes to review your hair history, discuss risks and benefits, and obtain your
        consent. You must disclose prior color, chemical services, allergies, sensitivities, and relevant
        conditions before service.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nothing on this website creates a medical relationship. If you are experiencing a medical
        emergency, call 911 or go to your nearest emergency room.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Hair services and consultations</h2>
      <p>
        Hair color, blonding, corrective work, and major style changes may require consultation before
        service. Timing, pricing, and maintenance guidance are determined based on hair history, goals,
        current condition, and the scope of work.
      </p>
      <p>
        Results vary based on hair condition, prior color history, home care, styling routine, and
        maintenance appointments.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Appointments &amp; cancellations</h2>
      <h3>Booking</h3>
      <p>
        Appointments are made through our booking portal or by contacting us directly. By booking an
        appointment, you agree to arrive on time and to complete any required intake forms truthfully and
        completely.
      </p>
      <h3>Cancellations &amp; no-shows</h3>
      <p>
        We ask for at least 24 hours notice for cancellations or rescheduling. Late cancellations or
        no-shows may result in a cancellation fee or forfeiture of any deposit paid.
      </p>
      <h3>Deposits</h3>
      <p>Certain high-material-cost services may require a non-refundable deposit at the time of booking.</p>
      <p>
        Deposits are applied toward the total service cost. They are non-refundable if you cancel
        within 24 hours of your appointment or fail to appear.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Payment</h2>
      <p>
        Payment is due at the time of service unless another arrangement is confirmed in writing.
        Prices are subject to change. The price quoted at your consultation is the price for that visit.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Assumption of risk &amp; informed consent</h2>
      <p>
        Hair and beauty services carry inherent risks including but not limited to color variation,
        dryness, breakage, scalp sensitivity, allergic reaction, dissatisfaction with results, or the need
        for additional appointments. By proceeding with any service, you acknowledge that you have had the
        opportunity to ask questions and provide your voluntary consent.
      </p>
      <p>You further acknowledge that no guarantee has been made regarding specific outcomes or results.</p>

      <h2>7. Photography &amp; social media</h2>
      <p>
        Before and after photos may be taken for your medical record. Use of your photos for marketing,
        social media, or website content requires your separate written consent. You may revoke consent at
        any time in writing. We will remove previously published content where reasonably practicable upon
        request.
      </p>
      <p>
        By tagging {c.business.name} on social media or submitting testimonials, you grant us a
        non-exclusive, royalty-free license to share that content (with your identity) on our platforms.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Website use</h2>
      <h3>Permitted use</h3>
      <p>You may use our website for lawful purposes only. You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Scrape, copy, or reproduce any website content without written permission</li>
        <li>Use the website in any way that could harm, disable, or impair our systems</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website</li>
        <li>Use the website to transmit spam, malware, or harmful content</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Intellectual property</h3>
      <p>
        All content on this website — including text, images, logos, graphics, and before/after photography
        — is the property of {c.business.legalName} or its licensors and is protected by copyright and
        other intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce or distribute any content without our
        prior written consent.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Third-party services</h2>
      <p>
        Our website may link to third-party services for booking, payment, maps, social media, or
        financing. Your use of these services is governed by their respective terms and privacy
        policies. We are not responsible for the practices, content, or security of third-party platforms.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p class="legal-doc__caps">
        TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, BOMBSHELL BEAUTY LAB, LLC SHALL NOT BE LIABLE
        FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED
        TO YOUR USE OF OUR WEBSITE OR SERVICES, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO LOST PROFITS, PERSONAL
        INJURY, OR PROPERTY DAMAGE.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our total liability to you for any claim arising from these Terms or your use of our services
        shall not exceed the amount you paid to us for the specific service giving rise to the claim.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Indemnification</h2>
      <p>
        You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless {c.business.legalName}, its owner, employees, and
        agents from any claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including attorney&apos;s fees) arising from:
        your use of our website or services, your violation of these Terms, your violation of any
        third-party rights, or any information you provide to us that is false or misleading.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of the state where {c.business.name} operates. Replace
        this placeholder with confirmed governing-law and venue language before launch.
      </p>

      <h2>13. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an
        updated &quot;Last Updated&quot; date. Your continued use of our website or services after any
        changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>14. Contact us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us:</p>
      <address class="legal-doc__address">
        <strong>{c.business.legalName}</strong><br />
        {addressLine}<br />
        Phone: <a href={`tel:${c.contact.phoneE164}`}>{c.contact.phone}</a><br />
        Email: <a href={`mailto:${c.contact.email}`}>{c.contact.email}</a><br />
        Website: <a href={c.url}>{siteHost}</a>
      </address>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-doc__header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .legal-doc__meta {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .legal-doc h2 {
    margin-block: 2.25rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--type-weight-display);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .legal-doc h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-doc h3 {
    margin-block: 1.25rem 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: var(--type-weight-body-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .legal-doc__important {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .legal-doc__caps {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: var(--type-weight-body-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 72ch;
  }
  .legal-doc p,
  .legal-doc li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }
  .legal-doc p + p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .legal-doc ul {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }
  .legal-doc li + li {
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
  }
  .legal-doc a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .legal-doc a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-hover);
  }
  .legal-doc__address {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
